text.section:
This subtitle, including the authority provided to the Commission under this subtitle, does not apply to:
lotteries conducted under Subtitle 1 of this title;
wagering on horse racing conducted under Title 11 of the Business Regulation Article;
the operation of slot machines as provided under Titles 12 and 13 of the Criminal Law Article; or
other gaming conducted under Titles 12 and 13 of the Criminal Law Article.
